- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses the use of deep learning models for detecting and mitigating adversarial attacks. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper mentions the use of deep learning models for image classification, which falls under the domain of computer vision. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the use of deep learning models for health management of industrial control systems and machinery.
